Nobiletin Delays Aging and Enhances Stress Resistance of Caenorhabditis elegans.

Yang X(1), Wang H(1)(2), Li T(3), Chen L(2), Zheng B(1)(4), Liu RH(3).

Author information:
(1)Overseas Expertise Introduction Center for Discipline Innovation of Food 
Nutrition and Human Health (111 Center), School of Food Science and Engineering, 
South China University of Technology, Guangzhou 510641, China.
(2)Ministry of Education Engineering Research Centre of Starch & Protein 
